Package com.github.hypfvieh.java.rtcompiler.resources.writer

Schnittstelle IResourceWriter

Alle bekannten Implementierungsklassen:
ByteArrMapResourceWriter, FileResourceWriter
public interface IResourceWriter
Base interface for all resource writers.
ResourceWriter are used to write any sort of resource to an OutputStream.
Seit:
1.0.0 - 2024-01-25
Autor:
hypfvieh

  • Methodenübersicht

    Modifizierer und Typ
    Methode
    Beschreibung
    OutputStream
    create(String _name)
    Creates an OutputStream pointing to the given resource name.
    The actual target of the OutputStream is specified by the implementation.
    The caller has to close the OutputStream after use.

    • create

      OutputStream create(String _name) throws IOException
      Creates an OutputStream pointing to the given resource name.
      The actual target of the OutputStream is specified by the implementation.
      The caller has to close the OutputStream after use.
      Parameter:
      _name - name of resource
      Gibt zurück:
      OutputStream
      Löst aus:
